                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18181202-55-off307 t18181202-55-crimeloc309"></join>. On the 30th of November, between eight and nine o'clock in the evening, the prisoner ran into the shop, took the soap off the<xptr type="pageFacsimile" doc="181812020031"></xptr>counter in the middle of the shop, and ran out. I followed and called out, Stop thief! He was taken on the other side of the way.</p>
